{
  "stem": "20616.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was very strict teacher and we often got the end of a-- a cane.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were hit, physical punishment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Today that would be called child abuse and would not be tolerated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But at that time, it was considered part of the educational process and we never questioned it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we always assumed that being hit was part of our education.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one thing, I always had an atrocious handwriting, I still do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he-- every time we signed a paper-- we-- we did a paper, he signed it with either a red C or a blue C.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And a red C it was passable and a-- a blue C was not acceptable.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Three blue Cs and you were marched up to the front, had to bend down, and you were hit quite hard with a cane.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And of course, other times, too-- if you misbehaved or neglected to do your homework, you were given physical punishment.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But aside from that, he was a wonderful teacher and a wonderful person and we learned a lot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he was a very kind person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was really not much of a scholar.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the four years of elementary school, I did fairly well in just about all subjects.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't even recall any-- I mean, we had German, some German history, geography, things like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't recall too much of the actual curriculum in public school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had music-- we had a different teacher for music.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And understand that the other-- one of the other teachers that taught the first grade, the first four grades, was a devout Nazi, a really convinced Nazi.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that time, that was still prior to the-- to Hitler and I never felt any kind of anti-Semitism or discrimination at all.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
